parameters.name: MET
parameters.description:
Mission elapsed time in seconds at the end of the
   accumulation.

parameters.name: WEDGE_DIGITIZER
parameters.description:
The wedge digitizer channel.  Taken together with 'strip'
   and 'zigzag' channels gives position on stop MCP:  x = wedge/(wedge + strip
   + zigzag).  See (3) for details.

parameters.name: STRIP_DIGITIZER
parameters.description:
The strip digitizer channel. Taken together with 'wedge'
   and 'zigzag' channels gives position on stop MCP:  y = strip/(wedge + strip
   + zigzag). See (3) for details.

parameters.name: ZIGZAG_DIGITIZER
parameters.description:
The zigzag digitizer channel. Taken together with 'strip'
   and 'wedge' channels gives position on stop MCP:  y = strip/(wedge + strip
   + zigzag). See (3) for details.

parameters.name: FIPS_MON_P15V
parameters.description: FIPS +15 volt monitor.

parameters.name: FIPS_MON_N15V
parameters.description: FIPS -15 volt monitor.

parameters.name: FIPS_MON_P5V
parameters.description: FIPS +5 volt monitor.

parameters.name: FIPS_MON_N5V
parameters.description: FIPS -5 volt monitor.

parameters.name: FIPS_MON_P35V
parameters.description: FIPS 3.5 volt monitor.

parameters.name: FIPS_MON_P25V
parameters.description: FIPS 2.5 volt monitor.

parameters.name: VREF_I2C_TEMP
parameters.description: FIPS VREF I2C temperature.

parameters.name: BH_BOT_I2C_TEMP
parameters.description: FIPS BH TOP I2C temperature.

parameters.name: BH_TOP_I2C_TEMP
parameters.description: FIPS BH TOP I2C temperature.

parameters.name: DS_HV_I2C_TEMP
parameters.description: FIPS DS-HV I2C temperature.

parameters.name: MON_MCP_HV
parameters.description:
Micro-channel plate high voltage (MCP-HV) monitor.
   Values:  0-16383.  Conversion:  219.73 mV/bit.

parameters.name: MON_PA_HV
parameters.description:
Post-acceleration high voltage (PA-HV) monitor.
   Values:  0-16383.  Conversion:  -915.53mV/bit.

parameters.name: MON_DS_HV
parameters.description:
Deflection system high voltage monitor.
   Values:  0..16383.  Conversion:  915.53mV/bit.

parameters.name: FIPS_STATUS
parameters.description:
FIPS status flag. Describes operational mode, individual
   HV enable/disable status and more. Convert back to binary notation to
   interpret the bit fields. See EPPS EDR SIS document for details.

parameters.name: FIPS_AUTO_SHUTDWN
parameters.description:
Clear FIPS autonomous hi-temperature shutdown flag.
   Allowed values: 0=do not clear (thus enabling autonomous hi-temp.
   shutdown).
   1=clear (thus disabling autonomous hi-temp. shutdown.  See (2)
   for details.

parameters.name: FIPS_HV_ALARM_SET
parameters.description:
FIPS software HV alarm monitor enable.  When enabled a
   particular HV supply will be disabled if the voltage monitor level for
   that supply exceeds the commanded value.  Allowed values: 0=disable
   software HV monitoring, 1=enable software HV monitoring. See (2)
   for details.

parameters.name: START_CFD_THLD
parameters.description:
Start constant fraction discriminator (CFD) Threshold.
   Allowed values: 0-255.

parameters.name: STOP_CFD_THLD
parameters.description:
Stop constant fraction discriminator (CFD) Threshold.
   Allowed values: 0-255.

parameters.name: PA_HV_SET
parameters.description:
Post-acceleration high voltage (PA-HV) setting.  Allowed
   values: 0-255. Conversion: -61.5234 V/bit.  Not to be set to less than 1/3
   of maximum, i.e., essentially allowed values are 82-255.

parameters.name: MCP_HV_SET
parameters.description:
Micro-channel plate high voltage (MCP-HV) Setting.
   Allowed values: 0..255.  Conversion: 14.7656 V/bit.  Not to be set to less
   than 1/3 of maximum, i.e., essentially allowed values are 82-255.

parameters.name: H_EVT_CNTRL_SET
parameters.description:
Proton event control settings.  Convert back to binary
   notation to interpret the settings. Bits 0-10 control H threshold.  If the
   TOF for an event is less than (or equal?) to this threshold, the event is
   classified as a proton.  Bits 12-15 control H proportion (decimation):
   0000=keep all proton events, 1111=keep 1 in 32768 H events.

parameters.name: TOF_CNTRL_SET
parameters.description:
Time of flight control settings.  Convert back to binary
   notation to interpret the bit settings.
     Bit 0 = half_perb
     Bit 1 = Cal_en
     Bit 2 = Fixwin_on
     Bit 3 = Tapsel1
     Bit 4 = Tapsel2
     Bit 5 = Srexclwin
     Bit 6 = Coreview
     Bit 7 = Intb_ext

parameters.name: STOP_RATE_COUNTER
parameters.description: Stop rate counter for one deflection voltage step.

parameters.name: STOP_RATE_STEP
parameters.description: Step at which stop rate counter was sampled.

parameters.name: I2C_READ_ADDR
parameters.description: Address of last raw I2C read from FIPS FPGA.

parameters.name: I2C_READ_VAL
parameters.description: Value of last raw I2C read from FIPS FPGA.
